quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,18,"Kala tawЙ—o ko o faandori golle makko moЖҙЖҙe Й—en, ko ngurndam aduna Й—am, hara o gonЙ—inaa fii laakara, o hittinaa fii mun, Men yaccinanay mo ka aduna ko Men Muuyi kon Menen, wanaa kanko ko o faalaa kon e neemaaji, refte Men waЙ—ana mo Jahannama o naata e magge Г‘alnde Darngal o sonnjora nguleendi magge, ko o ЕӢiГұaaЙ—o ko o suЙ“ori aduna kon o yeddi laakara, raЙ—aaЙ—o e yurmeende Alla."
  17,19,"Kala faandorЙ—o golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en mbarjaari laakara, o gollani Й—um golle laaЙ“uЙ—e ko jillaa e yiingo maa filli-filli, hara kadi himo gomЙ—ini huunde ko Alla wajinbini gomЙ—inngol kon ; Й“en siforЙ“e Й—in sifaaji, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en laatike jaЙ“aaЙ—e ka Alla, O yoЙ“ay Й“e Й—um."
  17,20,"MeЙ—en Й“eydana gooto-kala e feddeeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i (bonЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙo on), immorde e dokkal Joomi maa ngal -an NulaaЙ—o-, ko aldaa e taЖҙondiral. Dokkal Joomi maa ngal wonaali haЙ—eteengal e gooto, foti ko moЖҙЖҙo maa ko bonЙ—o."
  17,21,"Tasko -an NulaaЙ—o, ko honno Men Й“urniri yoga maЙ“Й“e e dow yoga aduna Й—oo ka arsike e darjaaji, ko laakara on Й“uri mawnude Й“ural darja e neema diini ngurdam aduna Й—am, ko ton kadi Й“uri Й“urdinndinal, yo gomЙ—inЙ—o on rerЙ—an Й—um."
  17,22,"Wata a waЙ—idan Alla -an jeyaaЙ—o on- reweteeЙ—o goo; wontoyaa ЕӢiГұaaЙ—o ka Alla,e jeyaaЙ“e Makko moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en jaarnoowo alanaama,ngona woppidaaЙ—o e Й—um mo maraa ballo."
  17,23,"Joomi maa yamirii ma an oo jeyaaЙ—o, O toЕӢi rewugol ko wonaa Kanko, O yamiri moЖҙЖҙagol e jibimЙ“e Й“en Й—iЙ—o ; tentinii non tuma Й“e yottii nayeegu : si goЙ—Й—o e mawЙ“e Й“en yottike nayeegu, maa Й“e Й—i Й—oo non Й“e nawyidii fewndo maa, wata a haaЙ“u haa haala hollirta a seytani, wata a gufu Й“e kadi wata a saЙ—tinamЙ“e konngol, wowlan Й“e konngol teddungol newiingol."
  17,24,"Yankinoran Й“e Й—igganngol Й“e e yurminngol Й“e, wi'aa: "Ko An yo Jooma, yurme Й“ee Й—iЙ—o yurminndee, sabu ko Й“e ne'i lan kon ka booboyaagal an"."
  17,25,"Joomi mon -ko onon yo yimЙ“e- ko O annduЙ—o ko woni kon ka fonndooji mooЙ—on immorde e laЙ“Й“inanngol Mo dewe Й—en e golleeji moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, e Й—igganngol jibinЙ“e Й“en Й—iЙ—o. si laatike annuyee mon e nder dewal mon ngal e huuwondiral mon moЖҙЖҙal ngal e jibinЙ“e on Й“en e tanaa maЙ“Й“e, Kanko Senaade wonanii Mo O wonii surroowo wonannde Й“en ruttotooЙ“e faade e Makko tuubuubuyee, on mo tuubi immorde e raЙ“Й“inЙ—inaare makko feЖҙЖҙunde nden e Й—oftagol Joomi makko maa jibinЙ“e mo Й“en Й—iЙ—o Alla suuЙ—anay mo."
  17,26,"Okku -an gomЙ—inЙ—o- Й“adondiraaЙ—o haqqee makko immorde e jokkugol enЙ—an e makko, okku Й“illiiЙ—o hatojinЙ—o, okku seteejo mo njooЙ“a mun lanni, wata a nafku jawdi maa ndin e nder goopol, maa e noone funsitugol."
  17,27,"Pellet naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en no ka goopi, funsooЙ“e Й“en ka nafkugol Й“e laatike musiЙ—Й“e seytanuuji Й—in, hiЙ“e Й—oftoo Й—i e huunde ko Й—i yamirta Й“e kon immorde e funsitugol e fantinngol."